
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>測驗分數</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "標楷體", Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 30px;
            width: 350px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative; 
        }

        .settings-icon {
            position: absolute;
            top: 10px;
            right: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .settings-icon:hover {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .container h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .button-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .button-list button {
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border: 2px solid #007bff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background-color: white;
            color: #007bff;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .button-list button:hover {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .button-list button:active {
            transform: scale(0.98);
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 12px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background-color: #6c757d;
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: #565e64;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="settings-icon" onclick="goToSettings()">⚙️</div>

        <h1>測驗分數</h1>
        <div class="button-list">
            <button onclick="goToPage('/support_assessment')">生產支持知覺量表</button>
            <button onclick="goToPage('/attachment_support')">親子依附支持量表</button>
            <button onclick="goToPage('/knowledge')">母乳知識量表</button>
            <button onclick="goToPage('/dour')">產後憂鬱量表</button>
            <button onclick="goToPage('/hurt')">疼痛量表</button>
            <button onclick="goToPage('/sleep')">匹茲堡睡眠品質量表</button>
        </div>

        <br>

        <div class="buttons">
            <button class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="goBack()">返回個資</button>
        </div>

        <script>
            function goBack() {
            window.location.href = '/result'; // 返回主頁面
        }
        </script>


    </div>

    <script>
        function goToSettings() {
            window.location.href = '/settings'; // 跳轉到設定頁面
        }

        function goToPage(page) {
            window.location.href = page;
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>